                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>your remittance I explained<lb/> that my last work \"House<lb/>\n                                        Influence a Sale for Mothers and daughters\" is <hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">not</hi> published<lb/> at my own\n                                        expense–The profits<lb/> whatever they may be are to<lb/> be\n                                        divided between my<lb/> publisher (who has taken the<lb/>\n                                        whole risk) myself–therefore<lb/> I should be glad if they\n                                        book could<lb/> get a circulation in\n                                                  <placeName>America</placeName><lb/> but I could\n                                        not send them<lb/> out. <persName>Mrssrs Carey\n                                                  Hart</persName>, if<lb/> they <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >really</hi> wish for theirs<lb/> must write\n                                        themselves to<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Miss Greenbridge</persName> Sons<lb/>\n                                        <placeName>5 Patornostor low Cheapside<lb/>\n                                                  London</placeName>– their order will<lb/> of\n                                        course be attended to<lb/> I will enclose with this</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3qv3cw2f/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
